      "message": "This is what I asked in the corresponding JIRA ticket. As I need to call AAI APIs in my container, I need to make sure that I could get the right URL within the container. I don't know if those values are injected into Holmes' container by any mechanism, or if there are some other ways to get the AAI URL. So I chose to pass them in through environment variables.",
